        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><placeName>Lexington </placeName><date when="1807-12-10">10th Decr 1807</date></p>
<p>1720lbs Bar Lead</p>

<p>Three months after date, I promise to pay <persName>Lewis Sanders</persName> or order,
Seventeen hundred and Twenty pounds of Small bar Lead, for value
Received to be delivered in <placeName>Lexington Kentucky</placeName>&#8212;</p>

<p>$72                                                 Moses Austin &amp; Co    [Rubric]</p>

<p>Received of <persName>Charles Carr</persName> the Above note in full <date when="1808-07-06">July 6 1808</date></p>

<p><persName>L. V. Hawkins</persName>
for <persName>Lewis Sanders</persName></p>
<p>Recd. <date when="1808-04-15">15th Apr.</date> 1635lbs bar Lead</p>
<p>[Endorsed]   Note N° 2</p>
<p><persName>Moses Austin</persName> <date when="1807-12-10">10th Decm. 1807</date></p>
<p>Due <date when="1808-03-10">10th March 1808</date></p>

        </div1>
